    <node id="Маленький принц">
      <data key="d0">Маленький принц</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Маленький принц is variously described as an unnamed character, a young prince lost in space and time from a desert, a human individual in a text about The Little Prince, one of many unnamed princes from different versions or interpretations of the story, a prince listening to conversations with two gryphs and a three-color beetle, a prince who is also talking about a gryph, a prince who has a conversation with someone about the character "Gnome", and as simply the main character in The Little Prince novella. There are conflicting descriptions suggesting he might be part of multiple versions or retellings, but the core essence remains a young human character navigating life's complexities through various encounters and conversations.&lt;SEP&gt;Young prince from the text who speaks and expresses emotions.&lt;SEP&gt;Unnamed prince in the text&lt;SEP&gt;Human individual, author of a literary work "The Little Prince"&lt;SEP&gt;The main character who is initially confused by the chaste lover and eventually leaves due to his lack of empathy.</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-6b2ba88f29d6d77fed85771bc5dc9981-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-6b2ba88f29d6d77fed85771bc5dc9981-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-adc6c168dbb425d9ece24d5bc28b2fcc-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-adc6c168dbb425d9ece24d5bc28b2fcc-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-1b8b1d20aa2c3a367e6898ef909e1830-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-7ff80b28ae61d87cbbd16fc2977b0881-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a4e544d8de8adf2c2d92737023d20063-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a4e544d8de8adf2c2d92737023d20063-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-483c61454a03ee080cf5d72363c83c1b-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-80bf0fd8d2ff27add315189775433556-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-80bf0fd8d2ff27add315189775433556-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-80bf0fd8d2ff27add315189775433556-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-80bf0fd8d2ff27add315189775433556-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-f22f66c8caa291e65e02b802daf878c8-chunk-000</data>
