      <data key="d2">He attempts to gain attention through simple gestures.&lt;SEP&gt;He continues to make gestures despite being ignored.&lt;SEP&gt;He finally gets bored of the repetitive gestures.&lt;SEP&gt;He attempts to engage with him on his terms.&lt;SEP&gt;He asks if the prince admires him.</data>
