    <edge source="He" target="Chaste_Love">
      <data key="d7">453.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The prince acknowledges his admiration, making him feel better.&lt;SEP&gt;Leaving due to feeling ignored, he feels compelled to leave.&lt;SEP&gt;Leaving out of boredom, he decides it's time for him to go.&lt;SEP&gt;He acknowledges him as a fan, making him feel better.&lt;SEP&gt;Finally, the prince acknowledges him as a fan.&lt;SEP&gt;He realizes he doesn't have much to offer.</data>
